[{"id":"VR856022","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<div><div class=\"stimulus_reference\"><div class=\"standalone_image\"><img alt=\"The figure shows a diagram consisting of, from left to right along a horizontal line, an object at point X, an object at point Y, and a convex mirror. The distance between point X and the mirror is 2 f. The distance between point Y and the mirror is 1.5 f.\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/578/VR856022.g02.svg\"/></div></div></div><p class=\"stem_paragraph\">An object is placed on the principal axis of a convex lens of focal length <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"f\"><math alttext=\"f\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi>f</mi></math></span></span>, as shown in the figure. The object, represented by the arrows in the figure, is first at location <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"X\"><math alttext=\"X\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>X</mtext></math></span></span> at a distance of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"2 f\"><math alttext=\"2 f\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn><mi>f</mi></math></span></span> from the lens, and the resulting image has a height of magnitude <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"h sub X\"><math alttext=\"h sub X\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>h</mi><mtext>X</mtext></msub></math></span></span>. The object is then moved to location <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"Y\"><math alttext=\"Y\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mtext>Y</mtext></math></span></span> at a distance of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1.5 f\"><math alttext=\"1.5 f\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1.5</mn><mi>f</mi></math></span></span> from the lens, and the resulting image has a height of magnitude <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"h sub Y\"><math alttext=\"h sub Y\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><msub><mi>h</mi><mtext>Y</mtext></msub></mstyle></math></span></span>. What is the ratio <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"Ratio h sub Y, to h sub X\"><math alttext=\"Ratio h sub Y, to h sub X\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><msub><mi>h</mi><mtext>Y</mtext></msub><mo>:</mo><msub><mi>h</mi><mtext>X</mtext></msub></mstyle></math></span></span>?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VR856022_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the ratio 1 to 2\"><math alttext=\"the ratio 1 to 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn><mo>:</mo><mn>2</mn></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the ratio 2 to 1\"><math alttext=\"the ratio 2 to 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn><mo>:</mo><mn>1</mn></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the ratio 1.5 to 2\"><math alttext=\"the ratio 1.5 to 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1.5</mn><mo>:</mo><mn>2</mn></math></span></span></p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the ratio 2 to 1.5\"><math alttext=\"the ratio 2 to 1.5\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>2</mn><mo>:</mo><mn>1.5</mn></math></span></span></p>"],"answer":1}]